OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss says he was not
OL,4,C'clever' enough to question Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FA former Post Office chief executive
OL,8,Fhas said he was not "clever" enough to
OL,9,Fask what challenges were made to the
OL,10,FHorizon IT system during a civil case
OL,11,Fagainst a subpostmistress ` despite
OL,12,Fbeing aware of the potential loss of
OL,13,F#1 million.
OL,15,FDavid Mills, the former chief
OL,16,Fexecutive of Post Office, admitted he
OL,17,Fshould have asked more questions about
OL,18,Fwhat was going on as concerns were
OL,19,Fraised as early as 1999.
