OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FSpeaking at the Horizon IT inquiry on
OL,8,FTuesday, Mills said he had seen a Post
OL,9,FOffice "IT risk register" suggesting
OL,10,Fthe organisation could suffer #1
OL,11,Fmillion worth of financial and
OL,12,Freputational damage if it lost a civil
OL,13,Fcase against a sub-postmaster.
OL,15,FThe establishment was pursuing sub-
OL,16,Fpostmaster Julie Wolstenholme who ran
OL,17,Fa branch in Cleveleys, Lancashire for
OL,18,F#25,000 through the civil court in
OL,19,F2003.
