OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FIndependent IT expert Jason Coyne, had
OL,8,Fwritten a report pointing out the
OL,9,FHorizon system was "clearly defective"
OL,10,Fas part of that case.
OL,12,FBut when asked in front of the post
OL,13,Foffice inquiry on Tuesday whether he
OL,14,Fhad asked what the challenge regarding
OL,15,Fthe Horizon system was, Mr Mills
OL,16,Fresponded: "no."
OL,18,FAsked why not, the former chief
OL,19,Fexecutive said: "I wasn't that clever.
OL,20,FI'm sorry, I didn't ask about it."
