OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss says he was not
OL,4,C'clever' enough to question Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FHe said the reason he did not notice
OL,8,Fthe miscarriage of justice developing
OL,9,Fwas because he was too busy trying to
OL,10,Fsave the Post Office business.
OL,12,FHe was asked if the Post Office was in
OL,13,F"real trouble" due to its online
OL,14,Faccounting system.
OL,16,FMr Mills replied: "Definitely, crisis
OL,17,Fmode it would have been in." The Post
OL,18,FOffice has come under fire since the
OL,19,Fbroadcast of ITV drama Mr Bates vs The
OL,20,FPost Office, which put the Horizon
OL,21,Fscandal under the spotlight.
