OL,4,C'clever' enough to question Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FMore than 700 sub-postmasters were
OL,8,Fprosecuted by the government-owned
OL,9,Forganisation and handed criminal
OL,10,Fconvictions between 1999 and 2015 as
OL,11,FFujitsu's faulty Horizon system made
OL,12,Fit appear as though money was missing
OL,13,Fat their branches.
OL,15,FHundreds of sub-postmasters are
OL,16,Fawaiting compensation despite the
OL,17,FGovernment announcing that those who
OL,18,Fhave had convictions quashed are
OL,19,Feligible for #600,000 payouts.
